def isprime(n):
    if n==1:
        return False
    if n==2:
        return True    
    for i in range(2, (n//2)+1):
        if(n%i==0):
            return False
    else:
        return True

def fun_nth_smithnumber(n):
    count=0
    ev=1
    re = 0
    while(n+1!=count):
        if(smith(ev)==True):
            count+=1
            re = ev
        ev+=1
    return re
